---
title: Pear, Farro, Walnut and Chicken Breast Salad with Goat Cheese and Maple-Rosemary Sweet Potatoes
description: This bountiful plate is not just another salad. Fresh pears and earthy, maple-rosemary roasted sweet potatoes add a touch of natural sweetness to complement the nutty farro and peppery arugula. Goat cheese and toasted walnuts provide ideal topping textures to ensure this abundant salad is a weeknight winner.
